description:
This is a 21 minute workout called 'Babywearing Postpartum Workout (Exercise With Baby) 20-Minute Postnatal Workout' from the channel Pregnancy and Postpartum TV.
The workout falls under Cardio/Mat and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Comfort Moves vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Join me for this 20-minute babywearing workout/postpartum workout (Exercise with baby)! You can get a good postnatal workout in while baby enjoys (or even falls asleep).
